title: The Case Against Adnan Syed - Addendum 1 – The Case for Adnan Syed
description:
March 14, 2019 / Jon Cryer is back to host our first addendum covering HBO's docuseries. He is joined by Susan, Colin, and guest panelist Krista Remmers as they discuss episode 1 of #thecaseagainstadnansyed.

Episode scoring music by Animal Weapon and Blue Dot Sessions.

Today’s Addendum is sponsored by Honeybook.
